64
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,680
She let everyone know

65
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:31,360
that Zhang Yuan was her enemy.

66
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,830
In such situations,

67
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:36,040
people tend to say things

68
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,840
that serve their own interests,

69
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
but Mei Zheng did just the opposite.

70
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,930
I've considered many possibilities.

71
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:45,190
I believe

72
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:46,720
