another person under suspicion.

74
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,409
Another person who's connected to
Zhang Yuan's case

75
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,880
and who they don't want us to discover?

76
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,870
To make an analogy, it's like...

77
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,980
