00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,510
and you're good at expressing yourself.

288
00:20:35,510 --> 00:20:37,510
If the police come to ask questions,

289
00:20:37,790 --> 00:20:39,190
try to remain objective,

290
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:40,530
but don't say too much.

291
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:42,440
Let's get this matter over with quickly.

292
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,100
Do you understand what I mean?

293
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,640
The teacher asked me
to talk to the police.

294
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,030
I'm scared to death.

295
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,640
What am I supposed to say?

296
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:56,480
Don't you know
what kind of person Mei Zheng is?

297
00:20:58,510 --> 00:20:59,000
[Recording]

298
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:02,830
She's just a tart.

299
00:21:04,550 --> 00:21:06,160
Lots of people saw her

300
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,920
taking older boys

301
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:09,700
to the library for dates.

302
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:12,300
She looks harmless,

303
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:16,310
but she seduced men secretly.

304
00:21:17,590 --> 00:21:18,750
Not only Zhou Lin,

305
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:20,680
but also Li Mufeng.

306
00:21:20,790 --> 00:21:21,790
These two guys

307
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:24,720
must have thought they were
her official boyfriend.

308
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,550
Otherwise, why would they fight?

309
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,400
I heard

310
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,310
she's also very close

311
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:31,040
to a university professor now.

312
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:32,240
Who knows,

313
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:35,000
maybe she deliberately made
those two boys fight each other

314
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:36,640
to get rid of them.

315
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,480
Mei Zheng,

316
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,590
please try to recall carefully.

317
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,790
On June 28, 2009,

318
00:21:44,790 --> 00:21:46,070
at 5 PM,

319
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:48,880
at the library next to
Wuyan Third High School,

320
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,510
what exactly did you see?

321
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:53,920
Was Zhou Lin doing anything to you then?

322
00:21:57,200 --> 00:22:00,070
He blocked me between the bookshelves

323
00:22:01,510 --> 00:22:02,970
and wouldn't let me leave.

324
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,300
Did you try to break free from him?

325
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:06,480
Yes,

326
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,530
I tried to get away from him.

327
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:10,080
But he... at that time he...

328
00:22:10,510 --> 00:22:11,880
he was grabbing my hand.

329
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,200
He grabbed your hand,

330
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:15,110
and then what did he do to you?

331
00:22:15,270 --> 00:22:17,640
He... He kept holding my hand.

332
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,640
He wouldn't let go.

333
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,970
He wouldn't release me.

334
00:22:20,110 --> 00:22:21,480
I was... I was very scared.

335
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,440
I was terrified.

336
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,070
I didn't know what to do.

337
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:24,310
I kept... kept shouting.

338
00:22:24,310 --> 00:22:25,240
I told him to let me go.

339
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,350
I kept yelling.

340
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,440
Then what else did Zhou Lin do to you?

341
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,380
I was scared.

342
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,260
I was so scared then.

343
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,070
I...

344
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,110
He...

345
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:37,790
He...

346
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:42,240
His expression was terrifying,

347
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,970
and he wasn't saying anything.

348
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,240
Then...

349
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,550
Then... then...

350
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,440
I...

351
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:50,790
I...

352
00:22:52,920 --> 00:22:55,160
I... I... I called for help.

353
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:58,170
Let me summarize your key testimony.

354
00:22:58,270 --> 00:22:59,640
-We need you to confirm…
-Stop.

355
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:00,480
Okay?

356
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,510
I'm begging you.

357
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:08,160
I want to forget what happened that day.

358
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:12,150
I want to erase everything
that happened that day.

359
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:17,240
I made mistakes over 10 years ago.

360
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:22,750
Those mistakes

361
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,480
have hurt you

362
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:27,400
and have hurt her

363
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:28,720
even more.

364
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,540
These works of yours are really good.

365
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:44,350
Have you thought about
holding a solo exhibition?

366
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,690
I have some materials here.

367
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:48,270
Take a look.

368
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:53,110
[Qi Art Museum]

369
00:23:53,110 --> 00:23:54,350
As long as you decide to do it,

370
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:55,680
the time, location

371
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:58,000
