372
00:23:58,510 --> 00:24:00,370
I can arrange everything for you.

373
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:03,260
But I haven't done anything special.

374
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:07,830
The fact that you don't hate Duan Hongshan
is already something remarkable.

375
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:10,430
We should all be grateful to you,
