395
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:25,830
He said

396
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:29,120
I never peeled asparagus when I cooked it.

397
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:31,710
Zhang Yuan would have found me eventually,

398
00:25:31,880 --> 00:25:34,340
